                    <comment id="12322390" author="john.wang@gmail.com" created="Wed, 18 May 2005 11:50:16 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Created an attachment (id=15064)&lt;br/&gt;
NullQuery, which just returns all documents in the index each with initial&lt;br/&gt;
